name: History’s Greatest of All Time with Peyton Manning
original_name: History’s Greatest of All Time with Peyton Manning
overview: Peyton Manning asks 100 experts in various categories to rank each greatest-of-all-time contender using statistics, innovation and legacy as criteria.

episodes.name: Stadium Smackdown
episodes.overview: From the Roman Colosseum to Wrigley Field, host Peyton Manning counts down the top ten stadiums of all time, as voted on by a panel of experts. Will your favorite make the list?

episodes.name: Fast and Furious Face-Off
episodes.overview: Host Peyton Manning counts down the top 10 sports cars of all time as voted on by a panel of experts.

episodes.name: Candy Clash
episodes.overview: Host Peyton Manning takes viewers through the top 10 candies of all time.

episodes.name: Invention Showdown
episodes.overview: From the light bulb to the automobile, these innovations changed the world. Host Peyton Manning unveils the top ten inventions of all time, as voted on by a panel of experts. Which one do you think made the biggest impact?

episodes.name: Dueling Daredevils
episodes.overview: From Evel Knievel to Harry Houdini, host Peyton Manning counts down the top ten daredevils of all time, as voted by a panel of experts. Which of these record-breaking, adrenaline junkies gets your heart pumping?

episodes.name: Titan Takedown
episodes.overview: Host Peyton Manning counts down the game-changing entrepreneurs whose contributions to media, tech and finance have earned them the title: Titans of Industry. From Oprah Winfrey to Jeff Bezos to JP Morgan which of these Titans did our panel of experts deem the greatest of all time?

episodes.name: Toy Wars
episodes.overview: From G.I. Joe to the Slinky, host Peyton Manning counts down the top ten toys, as voted by a panel of experts; discussing which childhood favorite will be crowned the best of the best.
